te, online course, product or service. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:image {\"id\":7533,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"https://alphaomegadigital.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/Avatar-27-1024x621.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-7533\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Explainer/animated videos </li><li>Content research</li><li>Content writing</li><li>Content planning/calendar </li><li>social media videos </li><li>social media posts</li><li>Email marketing content </li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"medium\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">This is not an exhaustive list. Marketing is an ever changing and rapidly growing industry, and trends will continue to come and go. The most important thing is being consist</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:atomic-blocks/ab-layouts /-->','Content Marketing','','inherit','closed','closed','','7430-revision-v1','','','2020-08-03 06:35:52','2020-08-03 06:35:52','',7430,'https://alphaomegadigital.com.au/7430-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(7546,1,'2020-08-03 21:49:22','2020-08-03 21:49:22','\n.front-page-2 .wrap {\n    display: flex;\n	\n    flex-wrap: wrap;\n	padding-right: 30px;\n	padding-left: 30px;\n	\n}\n.front-page-2 .widget {\n	padding-left: 50px;\n	padding-right: 50px;\n}\n.front-page-2 .widget .wpicon {\n	margin-bottom: 30px;\n}\n.front-page-2 .widget-title {\n    margin: 0.5rem auto 1rem;\n    font-size: 1em;\n    font-family: \"poppins\";\n}\n.button.white:hover {\n	background-color: #484dff;\n	color: white;\n}\n@media (min-width: 768px)\n.front-page-3 .entry:first-of-type {\n    width: 25%;\n}\n\n@media (min-width: 768px)\n	.front-page-4 .wrap {\n display: flex;\nflex-direction: row;}\n	\n}\n\n.site-footer {\n	background: #001632;\n	color: white; }\n.site-f