nt/uploads/2020/09/web-design-video-ao.mp4\"></video></figure>\n<!-- /wp:video -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns {\"className\":\"has-2-columns\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns has-2-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":1} -->\n<h1>Alpha + Omega </h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Alpha + Omega digital is an integrated marketing agency that provides businesses with a complete marketing solution and full service offering. Alpha and Omega in the Greek alphabet also translates to beginning to end, or A - Z. So in a nutshell, the service we usually provide is a marketing system for small businesses which encompasses your website, content marketing, social media and paid search.  Website integrations like Zapier, Zendesk, Mailchimp, Woocommerce mean that the administrative side of this process is tidy, and fully automated for you. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Let\'s take a look at how this process works in real time, after your project has been completed:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list {\"ordered\":true} -->\n<ol><li>Your website, social media, email</li><li>The free offer or competition we have created for your business is posted on your blog, and promoted heavily on social media with an opt in to gain email subscribers, and followers.</li><li>The offer is sent out to existing email subscribers</li><li></li></ol>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>1.) StrategyMarket analysis, brand positioning, research assimilation, testing and media strategy, etc.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>2.) CreativeBrand engineering, concept development, copywriting, graphic design and studio work, etc.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>3.) DataData strategy and analysis, customer profiling segmentation, data modeling, list procurement, etc.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>4.) CommunicationsPrint, social and mobile media, direct mail and email, online display, websites, DRTV, etc.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>5.) InteractiveWebsite design and application development, email marketing/post-lead nurturing, A/B and multivariate testing, paid search services and paid search management.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>6.) ProductionComplete data processing, offset and digital printing, mail piece personalization, web development and hosting, lead qualification and distribution.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>7.) AnalyticsSmart response capture systems, simple or comprehensive reporting, dynamic business intelligence.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column {\"width\":66.66} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\" style=\"flex-basis:66.66%\"><!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>About Me</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>I have 15 years experience in advertising and marketing working for various companies, and over time I realised the part I love most is working with clients. I want to know what makes you tick, why you got into business and what your challenges are. Most of all, I want us to solve those challenges together. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>I mostly work solo.</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>For most clients and services offered, I do all the work. There are exceptions to this though. The first, would be times when there is more work than I can reasonably handle. The second, is complementary services I outsource such as graphic design or videography. In these cases, I would outsource that work to a local talent who I trust to help my clients achieve quality work. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!--