alphaomegadigital.com.au/7686-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(7768,1,'2020-09-14 02:20:01','2020-09-14 02:20:01','Jane\nJames\nalphaomegadigitalau@gmail.com\nJane James','alphaomegadigitalau@gmail.com','','publish','closed','closed','','alphaomegadigitalau-gmail-com','','','2020-09-14 02:20:01','2020-09-14 02:20:01','',0,'https://alphaomegadigital.com.au/?post_type=flamingo_contact&#038;p=7768',0,'flamingo_contact','',0),(7677,1,'2020-09-28 04:20:08','2020-09-28 04:20:08','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Applications have just closed for the third round of the Banyule business grants scheme. Most businesses in Banyule by now would\'ve applied for the $5000 business grant. There was also a $2500 grant for business coaching services, that was a seperate financial pool to the main business grant scheme. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>This grant is specifically for local businesses impacted by covid who want to bring their products/service online and open up their potential customer base to other areas. For most businesses, that is going to mean building a site with an E-Commerce function, or a digital marketing campaign- most likely ad words, and targeted social media advertising to promote their existing online store.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Round 3 <a href=\"https://banyulebusiness.com.au/covid19grants/\">closed</a> 22/9/2020, however Banyule has announced they\'re doing two further rounds at the start of 2021 - In February and March. 20% of the key selection criteria is local procurement- that is you get 20% of your mark awarded for finding a local provider for your services, within the Banyule area. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Of the round2 Banyule Business grants 30/61 applicants were awarded the $5000 grant to help their business develop and build revenue online, which is a pretty great strike rate if you ask me. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>I can attest as someone who applied for round 3 that the process, and application is about half a day\'s work, tops. The application officer is lovely, and they even provide a group Zoom meeting to advise applicants how to successfully write a grant- they\'re made it a no brainer for busy business owners, who lack experience in grant writing and council applications. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Will you be applying for round 4 and 5? What have you got to lose?</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Alpha Omega Digital is offering premium <a href=\"https://alphaomegadigital.com.au/web-development/\">web design</a>, <a href=\"https://alphaomegadigital.com.au/content-marketing/\">content</a> and <a href=\"https://alphaomegadigital.com.au/digitalmarketing/\">digital marketing</a> services in Banyule and I am more than happy to provide you a PDF quote on email if you\'d like to get in <a href=\"https://alphaomegadigital.com.au/contact-2/\">touch</a>. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Applying for the Banyule Business grants scheme?','','publish','open','open','','applying-for-the-banyule-business-grants-scheme','','','2020-09-28 04:20:09','2020-09-28 04:20:09','',0,'http://alphaomegadigital.com.au/?p=7677',0,'post','',0),(1059,1,'2018-07-24 12:15:04','2018-07-24 12:15:04','\n				\n								','006','\n				\n								','publish','closed','closed','','006','','','2018-07-24 12:15:04','2018-07-24 12:15:04','',0,'https://alphaomegadigital.com.au/?post_type=client&amp;p=1059',0,'client','',0),(1061,1,'2018-07-24 12:16:16','2018-07-24 12:16:16','\n				\n								','007','\n				\n								','publish','closed','closed','','007','','','2018-07-24 12:16:16','2018-07-24 12:16:16','',0,'https://alphaomegadigital.com.au/?post_type=client&amp;p=1061',0,'client','',0),(1063,1,'2018-07-24 12:22:26','2018-07-24 12:22:26','\n				\n								','008','\n				\n								','publish','closed','closed','','008','','','2018-07-24 12:22:26','2018-07-24 12:22:26','',0,'