 tops. The application officer is lovely, and they even provide a group Zoom meeting to advise applicants how to successfully write a grant- they\'re made it a no brainer for busy business owners, who lack experience in grant writing and council applications. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Will you be applying for round 4 and 5? What have you got to lose?</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Alpha Omega Digital is offering premium <a href=\"https://alphaomegadigital.com.au/web-development/\">web design</a>, <a href=\"https://alphaomegadigital.com.au/content-marketing/\">content</a> and <a href=\"https://alphaomegadigital.com.au/digitalmarketing/\">digital marketing</a> services in Banyule and I am more than happy to provide you a PDF quote on email if you\'d like to get in <a href=\"https://alphaomegadigital.com.au/contact-2/\">touch</a>. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Applying for the Banyule Business grants scheme?','','inherit','closed','closed','','7677-revision-v1','','','2020-09-28 04:20:08','2020-09-28 04:20:08','',7677,'https://alphaomegadigital.com.au/7677-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(7877,1,'2020-09-14 02:32:00','2020-09-14 02:32:00','<!-- wp:video {\"id\":7875} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-video\"><video autoplay controls loop src=\"https://alphaomegadigital.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/alpha-omega-digital-1.mp4\"></video></figure>\n<!-- /wp:video -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>Content Marketing</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":7565,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><a href=\"https://alphaomegadigital.com.au/content-marketing/\"><img src=\"http://alphaomegadigital.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/green-chameleon-s9CC2SKySJM-unsplash-1024x683.jpg\" alt=\"content writing\" class=\"wp-image-7565\"/></a></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image --></div>\n<