 works in real time, after your project has been completed:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list {\"ordered\":true} -->\n<ol><li>Your website, social media, email, CRM, Google analytics are connected via API\'s that communicate with each other, transfer data and send you notifications of actions required.  </li><li>All data sources get pulled into Databox for initial analysis and data board setup, goals are set at this stage as well. </li><li>We setup a free offer or competition we have created for your business and post it on your blog, promote it heavily on social media to gain email subscribers, and followers which redirects traffic back to your website. </li><li>The offer is sent out to existing email subscribers, further redirecting traffic back to your website. </li><li>Once at your website visitors will either opt in to your free or low cost offer for service based businesses, or ideally purchase products it at least initiate a chat for product based businesses.</li><li>Prospects who opted in to you offer, or engaged in chat are automatically sent as contacts to your Hubspot CRM for future re marketing. </li><li>The cycle ends, and begins again. </li></ol>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Being a full service offering, Alpha Omega digital caters to your budget and can offer different levels of business support, depending on your needs: </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>1.) StrategyMarket analysis, competitor research, keyword research, content research, testing and media strategy, etc.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>2.) Creative concept development, copywriting, mock ups, figma design, graphic design etc.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>3.) Data analysis in Databox, strategy, customer profiling segmentation, data modeling, list procurement, etc.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>4.) CommunicationsPrint, social and mobile media, direct mail and email, online display, websites etc.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>5.) Lead generationWebsite design, email marketing/post-lead nurturing, A/B split testing, paid search services and paid search management.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>7.) Post campaign analyticspost evaluation of date from engagement, visibility, increased subscribers, followers, open rate etc. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column {\"width\":66.66} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\" style=\"flex-basis:66.66%\"><!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>About Me</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>I have 15 years experience in advertising and marketing working for various companies, and over time I realised the part I love most is working with clients. I want to know what makes you tick, why you got into business and what your challenges are. Most of all, I want us to solve those challenges together. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>I mostly work solo.</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>For most clients and services offered, I do all the work. There are exceptions to this though. The first, would be times when there is more work than I can reasonably handle. The second, is complementary services I outsource such as graphic design or videography. In these cases, I would outsource that work to a local talent who I trust to help my clients achieve quality work and get the results they are after. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column {\"width\":33.33} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\" style=\"flex-basis:33.33%\" id=\"jane-profile\"><!-- wp:image {\"id\":7835,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"className\":\"is-style-rounded\"} -->\n<figure cla