hat work to a local talent who I trust to help my clients achieve quality work. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column {\"width\":33.33} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\" style=\"flex-basis:33.33%\" id=\"jane-profile\"><!-- wp:image {\"id\":7835,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"className\":\"is-style-rounded\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-style-rounded\"><img src=\"https://alphaomegadigital.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/jane-bw.jpg\" alt=\"Jane James BW\" class=\"wp-image-7835\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->','About Us','','inherit','closed','closed','','7688-revision-v1','','','2020-09-13 23:35:31','2020-09-13 23:35:31','',7688,'https://alphaomegadigital.com.au/7688-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(7865,1,'2020-09-13 23:41:54','2020-09-13 23:41:54','','web-design-video-ao-copy-1','','inherit','open','closed','','web-design-video-ao-copy-1','','','2020-09-13 23:41:54','2020-09-13 23:41:54','',7430,'https://alphaomegadigital.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/web-design-video-ao-copy-1.mp4',0,'attachment','video/mp4',0),(7870,1,'2020-09-13 23:50:27','2020-09-13 23:50:27','','content-marketing','','inherit','open','closed','','content-marketing-2','','','2020-09-13 23:50:27','2020-09-13 23:50:27','',7430,'https://alphaomegadigital.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/content-marketing.mp4',0,'attachment','video/mp4',0),(7881,1,'2020-09-14 02:35:36','2020-09-14 02:35:36','<!-- wp:video {\"id\":7829} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-video\"><video autoplay controls loop src=\"https://alphaomegadigital.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/web-design-video-ao.mp4\" playsinline></video></figure>\n<!-- /wp:video -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"textColor\":\"black\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-black-color has-text-color\">The type of service I offer is typically a Wordpress website that is built on the Genesis Framework. I use Genesis for my own sites, and mostly for client sites as well. Genesis delivers a high quality wordpress website that is SEO friendly and optimised for speed. Your site should ideally load in under 3 seconds and use a minimal amount of plugins in order to achieve this, and this is a marker I aim for when delivering a new web project. You can read more about why I use Genesis for my projects<a href=\"https://alphaomegadigital.com.au/why-i-use-the-genesis-framework\"> </a><strong><a href=\"https://alphaomegadigital.com.au/why-i-use-the-genesis-framework\">here</a>.</strong> </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Before we get to the how\'s of building a web project, I\'d like to walk you through the process from start to finish so you know what to expect and how much involvement is required </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>1. Client Brief</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Whether I\'m speaking with a client online or face to face, that first meeting is really about gathering information. Tell me your story. Why you got into this particular business. What are your current challenges? What do you like and dislike about your current website? What functions are you looking for? This is a genuine discussion where we uncover your needs, and what service offering is best going to match those needs. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>2. Design </h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>After uncovering your needs at our first meeting, I will request any asset files you have and wish to use and begin working on a site mockup for you. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>For <strong>bigger</strong> projects, you will get a design system in <a href=\"https://www.figma.com/\">Figma.</a> Usually we\'d start with a home page mockup, and if you are happy with the layout, I will then create additional pages for your site as well as as the responsive version. Your site will then be built using my Genesis starter theme. Yes it is still a child theme for Genesis, but there are no inherited styles or content, its a bare bones starter theme that merely has functions and a basic codebase to work off. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>For clients with a <strong>limited budget,</strong> I will create a one page style guide and you will receive a link to a staging domain where I will edit your existing Genesis child theme to match the styles and colours of the chosen child theme. There may be some modifications to your functions.php file, and perhaps some custom functions or custom post types but your site will not be highly modified. This is because you can basically modify a child theme to within an inch of its life, and heavy modifications of an existing child theme require just as much work as building a site from a starter theme. And the budget allocated to the project reflects the amount of work required. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>3. Development</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>This is the phase where your design and your style guide will be converted into code. You will be sent a development link and your site is deployed to a staging domain. This will allow you to see how your site is coming to fruition, and allows for a collaborative process between us to make sure you are completely happy with the look and feel of your site, and also add in any business functions you may wish to have such as Paypal integration, Mailchimp integration, Zapier, Zen desk and so on. Your site will also be continuously backed up with version control on Github, so if changes are made and you wish to revert to a previous version of the site the option is there to do so. You will be asked to provide the content- that is the pages and what is written to explain your service offering. If you aren\'t comfortable doing this, or don\'t have time I can do it for you for an additional charge. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>4. Deploy</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"textColor\":\"black\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-black-color has-text-color\">After you have approved your site and content on the staging domain, I will deploy your site to your domain using FTP client and your C Panel. I personally use and recommend <strong><a href=\"https://ventraip.com.au/\">Ventra IP</a> </strong>for secure and fast wordpress hosting, and if you arrange the hosting through us I will be able to login to your C panel in future if you require backups or updates. If you don\'t wish to do this, you can purchase your own hosting plan and give me access for the deployment process. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>5. Marketing</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>A misconception that commonly occurs amongst clients is that once their website is up and running, their phone will ring off the hook and this couldn\'t be more untrue. Yes your website is there to present your service/product to the internet and yes it will capture emails and integrate to your marketing database. However: if you do nothing to market your business online via social media, google adwords/shopping, social media advertising, content marketing and so on you are not doing anything to actively promote your business. Subsequently your traffic will be low, and your conversion rate even lower. If you want to be successful online, and within a short time period as opposed to a slow burn over ten years, you should expect to spend 5-10 times more on marketing than you did for your web project. Marketing is never going to be one single thing, but a combination of content marketing, social media, paid search, paid advertising and networking. If you can do all of these things successfully you will see good results over time. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Web Development','','inherit','closed','closed','','7432-revision-v1','','','2020-09-14 02:35:36','2020-09-14 02:35:36','',7432,'https://alphaomegadigital.com.au/7432-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(7867,1,'2020-09-13 23:42:54','2020-09-13 23:42:54','','web-design-video-ao-copy-1-1','','inherit','open','closed','','web-design-video-ao-copy-1-1','','','2020-09-13 23:42:54','2020-09-13 23:42:54','',7436,'https://alphaomegadigital.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/web-design-video-ao-copy-1-1.mp4',0,'attachment','video/mp4',0),(7888,1,'2020-09-15 04:16:30','2020-09-15 04:16:30','<!-- wp:video {\"id\":7867} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-video\"><video controls loop src=\"https://alphaomegadigital.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/web-design-video-ao-copy-1-1.mp4\"></video><figcaption>Everything has moved online in 2020. Have you?</figcaption></figure>\n<!-- /wp:video -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:atomic-blocks/ab-drop-cap {\"dropCapFontSize\":2} -->\n<div style=\"color:#32373c\" class=\"wp-block-atomic-blocks-ab-drop-cap drop-cap-letter ab-font-size-2 ab-block-drop-cap\"><div class=\"ab-drop-cap-text\"><p>The internet is such a big part of our lives now and it has completely changed the way in which we bank, shop, consume media and socialise. </p></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:atomic-blocks/ab-drop-cap -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Newspaper and magazine have become mostly <a href=\"https://www.crikey.com.au/2020/05/04/australia-magazines-disruption-bauer/\">defunct</a> in Australia, as readership has dwindled and advertising costs have remained high; needless to say this means advertisers have been paying the same advertising rates for a lesser result.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>TV advertising has also taken a <a href=\"https://www.adnews.com.au/news/digital-ad-spend-to-overtake-tv-in-2017-studies-find\">hit</a>; once considered the gold standard of effective advertising in Australia, ad free streaming services such as Netflix and Stan have drawn audiences away from mainstream TV. Audiences for years were frustrated with the increasing amount of ads on TV, but they tolerated it when no other options were available. Streaming services have provided a solution to this problem, thus creating a mass exodus from commercial TV. This applies to the embattled <a href=\"https://www.adnews.com.au/news/news-corp-s-billion-dollar-write-down-for-foxtel#:~:text=News%20Corp%20has%20written%20down,nearly%20%24US1%20billion%20(AUD1.&amp;text=27%20billion%20(AUD3.,of%20%24US1%20billion%20(AUD1.\">Foxte</a>l as well.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>These events mean Australian businesses are spending more money than ever on digital marketing: in 2017 we spent 3.43 billion advertising online, and in 2019 we spent a whopping <a href=\"https://www.adnews.com.au/news/australian-brands-spent-9-4-billion-on-digital-ads-in-2019\">9.4 billion</a>, which is significantly higher than the previous forecast of 4.97 billion for <a href=\"https://www.adnews.com.au/news/digital-ad-spend-to-overtake-tv-in-2017-studies-find\">2019</a>.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Aside from the obvious fact that digital marketing is now more effective than traditional media, it also offers a degree of transparency. You no longer have to place an ad and cross your fingers it works for you, all of the data is readily available through the many digital analytics platforms so you know exactly how each dollar translates into web traffic, social media traffic, engagement and sales. I use <a href=\"https://databox.com/\">databox</a> to track all of these metrics with clients. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>There is one caveat to my previous statement though: although transparency and data are a surety in the digital age, none of those metrics are guaranteed to translate into sales for your business. This presents a problem to the everyday business owner who is running their own digital campaigns. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>There is a sense of achievement and the feeling of being in control; you\'re spending money and you can see its resulting in extra likes to your page, more followers, more traffic, more page views. There is really only one question to ask yourself  at this point:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:quote {\"className\":\"is-style-large\"} -->\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote is-style-large\"><p>\"Are your current digital marketing efforts translating into sales?</p><p></p></blockquote>\n<!-- /wp:quote -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>If the answer is yes, then awesome keep doing what you\'re doing if you\'re happy with your figures. If the answer is no, then it\'s really time to engage with a professional to maximise the results you\'re getting for your ad spend. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>My goal when conducting digital campaigns for clients, at the very least is to cover my cost. That is the money you as the client spends on hiring me to manage your marketing is offset by the increase in results you attain from hiring a professional. This effect is also compounded by the fact that you now have a lot more time that you were spending on marketing, to other facets of your business. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns {\"className\":\"services-tabs\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns services-tabs\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>Google Analytics</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Google analytics gives us the data for your web traffic, organic search, paid search, keyword ranking, click through traffic from social and external URL\'s. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:image {\"id\":7600,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"https://alphaomegadigital.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/morning-brew-NrOUHQ2jHtU-unsplash-1024x683.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-7600\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns {\"className\":\"services-tabs\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns services-tabs\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:image {\"id\":7592,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"http://alphaomegadigital.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/stephen-phillips-hostreviews-co-uk-shr_Xn8S8QU-unsplash-1-1024x625.jpg\" alt=\"google adwords img alt\" class=\"wp-image-7592\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>Pay Per Click</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Google adwords, Google shopping, Bing search and Duck Duck go advertising give us real world data on impressions, CTR, page views, revenue and references. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns {\"className\":\"services-tabs\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns services-tabs\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>Ads Manager</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Facebook ads manager allows us to create effective and budget controlled Facebook and Instagram campaigns, filtering demographics by age, location, occupation, previous page views and competitor views. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:image {\"id\":7607,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"https://alphaomegadigital.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/austin-distel-tLZhFRLj6nY-unsplash-1024x683.jpg\" alt=\"Facebook advertising image\" class=\"wp-image-7607\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns {\"className\":\"services-tabs\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns services-tabs\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:image {\"id\":7613,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"http://alphaomegadigital.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/neonbrand-GCQaYDCQwgc-unsplash-1024x683.jpg\" alt=\"app advertising img\" class=\"wp-image-7613\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>App advertising</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Where relevant to your industry, advertising on apps of relational products and services can be an effective and somewhat cost efficient way to bring more traffic to your site.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->','Digital Marketing','','inherit','closed','closed','','7436-revision-v1','','','2020-09-15 04:16:30','2020-09-15 04:16:30','',7436,'https://alphaomegadigital.com.au/7436-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(7868,1,'2020-09-13 23:42:58','2020-09-13 23:42:58','<!-- wp:video {\"id\":7867} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-video\"><video autoplay controls loop src=\"https://alphaomegadigital.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/web-design-video-ao-copy-1-1.mp4\"></video><figcaption>Everything has moved online in 2020. Have you?</figcaption></figure>\n<!-- /wp:video -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:atomic-blocks/ab-drop-cap {\"dropCapFontSize\":2} -->\n<div style=\"color:#32373c\" class=\"wp-block-atomic-blocks-ab-drop-cap drop-cap-letter ab-font-size-2 ab-block-drop-cap\"><div class=\"ab-drop-cap-text\"><p>The internet is such a big part of our lives now and it has completely changed the way in which we bank, shop, consume media and socialise. </p></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:atomic-blocks/ab-drop-cap -->\n\n<!-- wp:pa